<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Electronic Private Prescription</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 2px;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .logo img {
        max-width: 170px;
        height: auto;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 26px;
        color: #4a4a4a;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #1b3f6d;
        color: #fff;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .clinic-details {
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        margin-top: 15px;
        padding-top: 10px;
      }

      .clinic-details h4 {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        color: #1b3f6d;
      }

      .clinic-info-line {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://public-consumables.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com/sendscript-logo.png" alt="SendScript Logo" />
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= patient_name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your consultation with <%= doctor_name %> at <%= clinic_name %>. Below is your electronic private prescription ID for your convenience.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Prescription ID:</strong> <%= prescription_id %></p>
        <h4>Patient Instructions:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Please present this Prescription ID to the responsible pharmacist at your preferred pharmacy.</li>
          <li>To retrieve your prescription, provide the pharmacist with the Prescription ID and your date of birth.</li>
          <li>Do not download or print the prescription. It will be processed electronically.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h4>Pharmacist Instructions:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Visit <a href="https://www.sendscript.com/dispense">www.sendscript.com/dispense</a></li>
          <li>Enter the Prescription ID and patient's date of birth to retrieve the prescription.</li>
          <li>Download the prescription and select "Dispensed" once you have processed it.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
        
        <p>Warm regards,</p>
        <div class="clinic-details">
          <h4>Clinic Information</h4>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Name:</strong> <%= clinic_name %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Address:</strong> <%= clinic_address %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>City:</strong> <%= clinic_city %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Postal Code:</strong> <%= clinic_postal_code %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Country:</strong> <%= clinic_country %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Tel:</strong> <%= clinic_mobile %></div>
          <div class="clinic-info-line"><strong>Email:</strong> <%= clinic_email %></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer"></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>